data.description: Price Reduced $245,000.00 Seller Motivated, Beautiful 4 PLEX, So many possibilities are yours with this 4,995 Sq ft Italian style home.  Situated on a Ridge Top 5.25 acres with Forever Views, this home has a Gated Entry, 9 foot ceilings, 7-8  Bedrooms, 5 Full Bathrooms, 4 fireplaces, 3 Car Garage, Infinity Edge Pool/Waterfall, Beach Entry, Built in Spa and Outdoor Shower.  At the present time, the home is divided into 4 Beautiful Apartments, 3 Units are now rented with a $6700 Mo. Income, ($80,400 Yr.) Tenants pay all utilities. Owner lives in 4th unit. Possible $10K Mo. ($120,000 Yr.) Income with all 4 Units rented. Each Unit has its Own Separate Outside Entry, Full Kitchen, Washer/ Dryer, Fire Place, Heat/Air unit. You can live in one and Rent the other 3 or rent all 4.  “Or”, if you want a large, Luxury Home just for yourself, you can bring the home back to its original layout of just under 5,000 SqFt. of Grand Living Space, the choice is yours. Take a look around, you won't find anything like this Beautiful 4 plex anywhere in San Diego County with this Awesome of a View, Location, Pool and Rented with Substantial Income, at this price.  Call, Text or email for further details.  Very Quiet and Peaceful Rural area, but close to everything. Less than 10 min. East of I-15 and Hwy 76, (Fallbrook area) Click on "Virtual Tour" just above Remarks area left side.
